name: .EPIBRW File Extension
summary: Learn about .EPIBRW files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Generic file extension for a file stored on a Microsoft IIS-based Web server; often used by .PDF files, but may also be used by several other file types.

content: Clicking on a link ending in ".epibrw" may display the file directly in a browser window or may initiate a download of the file.
